{"tid":814813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美白宮官員：支那是全球經濟的寄生蟲","createTime":"2018-09-11T13:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T17:12:02.000Z","uid":11148,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"92ae15816e2ff967c0feb9858d5f8b1fc538635b","tid":814813,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普正考慮對2670億美元的中國進口商品加徵額外關稅，白宮國家貿易委員會主任納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）在談到此事時，也怒斥中國是全球經濟的寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n據《福斯財經網》報導，納瓦羅在接受財經網電視節目《Lou Dobbs Tonight》採訪時，強調中國為了增長經濟所做的一切，都是以犧牲其他國家的利益為代價，所以中國就是世界的寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n另外，川普政府致力於減低中國對美國智慧財產權的剽竊，納瓦羅對此表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國正是靠著竊取智慧財產權來催化經濟成長</span>。納瓦羅還說，美國希望與中國建立公平對等的貿易關係，不過目前尚未達成。<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2547628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2547628&d=oKeebo5BtbW3C83STe0mjJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=70e9b8d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2547628&h=77a939a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2547628</a><br />\n<br />\n支那除左係寄生蟲仲係癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a2a928a3c5b3b833887a50685bb1024c9b6396","tid":814813,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"兜巴車埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe8ec3389eeae404b40375cfa0217a57def21ce","tid":814813,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bce03793aa3680b0adb9d4a9c6341f7dfc9d50a","tid":814813,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"